    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_432839">First off, this is NOT so that I can change current poisons, but to get a good survey of what is already here.  Yes this is in preparation for a revamp, but it is just the beginning stages and research.  I still have no actual time-lines to give you.  Also for now I am not looking for what to do with poison or these poisons, I am just gathering data.  I just want to be as sure as I can that I have complete data.<br />
<br />
I am also just looking for actual poison recipes that make poisons, not other things like extracts and augments made using the poison skill.<br />
<br />
Is there anything missing form the list bellow?  This is the list I found of recipes to make poisons in game.  (this is recipes... not actual poisons so I expect that some duplication in this list.)<br />
