</div>Well, I for one would like to be able to use a skill I have worked so hard to skill up, at great expense, and time... give a return on investment that so may others that skill up have been able to attain... I do want something to sell! Something fairly easy to make (when skill is added into the equation), it doesn't have to be worth tons of plat that price it out of affordability (oh, how I loved tha augs...) but can make a decent amount of plat, by selling to everyone, rather than just other rogues that have the same skill. When was the last time you got 500k pp just for doing a poison combine, succed or fail?<br />
The ideas of utility intrigue me... that would be worthwile, like Sloth and Shissar used to be. DPS is nice, but not as important. It would have been nice to have kept the ability to make current augs with more abundant drops, but the jewlcrafters have that toi themselves for now. Because you would have to admit it would be nice to hear in OOC, or guild chat &quot;Hey I need a GM Poison Crafter!&quot;?</div>
