 <br />
The reason I do not think poison will be revamped is that it encroaches into the other areas of the game. The other T/S basically make armor. This is a big part of the overall EQ picture and looked at by all the Devs. I am sure Ngreth gets guidelines on what can be done with this armor. <br />
